(99, 33, '/uploads/images/Code%20Scanner/V-checker%204%20in%201%20for%20bmw.jpg', 'V-checker 4 in 1 for bmw/toyota/vw/lexus', '<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" width="98%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					<strong>Brief introduction</strong> <br />\r\n					V-Scanner is the latest car diagnostic computer and diagnostic equipment which is specially designed for car maintenance technician. It has the function of reading fault code, reading data stream and the action test, and control features such as ECU coding, while the miniature mainframe, powerful diagnostic features, convenient on-line upgrade, the integration of multi-functional joints are maintenance technicians preferred. V-scanner is a standard vehicle maintenance equipment for technicians.</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong>Characteristic</strong></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					Auto diagnostic hardware is designed according to international standards, all the models are compatible with the diagnosis of the world interface. <br />\r\n					Powerful test can diagnose the car of the electric control system fault. <br />\r\n					Unique way to read the data stream, data refresh faster. <br />\r\n					Embedded operating system, open diagnostic platform, faster diagnosis. <br />\r\n					The integration of diagnostic connector, the appearance of small, rugged, reliable performance. <br />\r\n					Keyboard input methods, simple and quick operation.<br />\r\n					Perfect after-sales service system, customers enjoy one-on-one caring for life of service.<br />\r\n					Multi-language user interface, suitable for use all over the world.<br />\r\n					It supports upgrade through Internet.</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong>Supported Language</strong></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					Simple chinese, TRI Chinese, English, Spanish, Czechish, Portuguese, German, Russian and so on.</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong>Supported Car Model </strong></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					OBD-II and EOBD<br />\r\n		