e lastest BMW vehicles.&nbsp;<br />\r\n	2. MINI OPS is more stable than OPS. .&nbsp;<br />\r\n	3. MINI OPS is in less size and weight, so it can save lots of shipping freight and it is convenient to carry. <br />\r\n	</span></p>\r\n', 1258040711, 1258264512, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 1, '1', 'no'),
(125, 27, '/uploads/images/Professional%20diagnostic%20Kit/AD100.jpg', 'AD100', '<div style="margin: 1em 0px; clear: right;">\r\n	<div style="font-weight: bold;">\r\n		Description:</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>The World Leaders in Key Programming Systems</strong><br />\r\n		This is a piece of equipment you must have if you are an automotive locksmith, Car Repair shop, Car Accessories or even Car Dealer.<br />\r\n		Features:<br />\r\n		READS FAULT CODES <br />\r\n		CLEARS FAULT CODES <br />\r\n		DISPLAYS LIVE DATA <br />\r\n		COMPONENET ACTUATION <br />\r\n		READS IMMOBILISER ECU ID&rsquo;S <br />\r\n		READS MECHANICAL KEY CODES <br />\r\n		CLEARS KEY MEMORIES <br />\r\n		PROGRAMS NEW KEYS <br />\r\n		ECU IDENTIFICATION <br />\r\n		READS EKA CODES <br />\r\n		PROGRAMS NEW EKA CODES <br />\r\n		PROGRAMS PLIP KEYS</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>Largest range of Manufacturers</strong><br />\r\n		&bull; Ford &bull; LDV &bull; GM &bull; Isuzu &bull; VW &bull; Audi &bull; Seat &bull; Skoda &bull; Rover<br />\r\n		&bull; Land Rover&bull; Ford USA &bull; Chrysler &bull; Jeep &bull; Peugeot &bull; Citroen<br />\r\n		&bull; Nissan &bull; Jaguar &bull; Aston Martin &bull; Renault &bull; Mitsubishi &bull; Daewoo<br />\r\n		&bull; Hyundai &bull; Kia &bull; Fiat &bull; Alfa &bull; Lancia &bull; Honda &bull; Suzuki &bull; Toyota<br />\r\n		&bull; Proton &bull; Mazda &bull; Subaru &bull; Iveco &bull; Mercedes Sprinter/Vito<br />\r\n		&bull; BMW Mini <br />\r\n		<strong>new Version Increas：<br />\r\n		</strong>&bull;Toyota &amp; Lexus New systems added (Internal Test Only)<br />\r\n		&bull;Updates to Honda systems added (Internal Test Only)<br />\r\n		&bull;Santa Fe added to Hyundai menu.<br />\r\n		&bull;NISSAN NATS 5 System updated for PRO machines.<br />\r\n		&bull;HONDA Systems Type 9 and 10 added (Internal Test only)<br />\r\n		&bull;VAG CAN Pin code reading added to VAG CAN software.<br />\r\n		&bull;NATS 2_5 System, Dongle F added to the PRO system.<br />\r\n		&bull;Grandis added to M