(176, 35, '/uploads/images/Vag%20Diagnostic%20Kit/VAG%20IMMO%201+3%20Code%20Reader.jpg', 'VAG IMMO 1+3 Code Reader', '<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">VAG IMMO 1+3 Code Reader<br style="" />\r\n	VAG IMMO 1+3 Code Reader : Reads VAG the IMMO3 security system to take the memory in engine ECU PIN CODE;Reads AUDI old IMMO BOX PIN CODE ;Cannot read takes VAG IMMO2 system PIN CODE ;VAG (AUDI-VW-SEAT-SKODA) immobiliser Login Code...... <br style="" />\r\n	Product Name:&nbsp; VAG IMMO 1+3 Code Reader<br style="" />\r\n	Part No.:&nbsp; AE006<br style="" />\r\n	Net Weight:&nbsp; 0.25KG </font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Features:</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">VAG PIN CODE READER<br style="" />\r\n	VAG PIN CODE IMMO1+IMMO3<br style="" />\r\n	Reads takes VAG IMMO3 and old AUDI IMMO BOX by the OBDII diagnosis connection</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Support cars: <br style="" />\r\n	AUDI&nbsp;&nbsp; PASSAT&nbsp;&nbsp; BORA&nbsp;&nbsp; GOLF&nbsp;&nbsp; POLO&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AUDI-IMMO BOX</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Reads VAG the IMMO3 security system to take the memory in engine ECU PIN CODE.<br style="" />\r\n	Reads AUDI old IMMO BOX PIN CODE<br style="" />\r\n	Cannot read takes VAG IMMO2 system PIN CODE<br style="" />\r\n	VAG (AUDI-VW-SEAT-SKODA) immobiliser Login Code<br style="" />\r\n	(Secret Key Code)Reader and Key Learning Connects by OBDII with PC</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Type of cars:</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Audi old to 1997</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Audi A4,A6 1997-1998 VDO</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Audi A3,A4,A6 VDO 1999--&gt;</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Audi A3,A4,A6 MM 1999--&gt;</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Audi TT</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">SEAT</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Passat,Golf IV Moto Meter</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">VW Golf IV,Passat B5 VDO</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">VW Beetle</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">VW VDO 1999--&gt;</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Passat Magneti Marelli</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">VW Passt B6,Golf IV,Polo<br style="" />\r\n	</font></p>\r\n', 1258291707, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 1, '1', 'no'),
(177, 35, '/uploads/images/Vag%20Diagnostic%20Kit/VAG%20IMMO3.jpg', 'VAG IMMO3 ', '<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;"><strong style="font-family: Arial;">Features:</strong><br style="" />\r\n	&bull; Interface connects to RS232 of PC <br style="" />\r\n	&bull; Read IMMO Login code from supported VAG cars via diagnostic connector <br style="" />\r\n	&bull; Key learning and adaption via diagnostic connector </font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font style="font-family: Arial;">Using this device you can read the security Login Code for VAG Cars who are made starting +/- June 2000 to year 2004 and who are using ImmoBiliser System 3.<br style="" />\r\n	Cars models before year 2000 have an older immobiliser system where a Login Code is not integrated in Engine ECU. These old model cars also need a Login Code to program new keys, but in that case you need another Login Code Reader, where a Login Code can be simply read from Instrument Cluster. This login reader can be bought from us too.<br style="" />\r\n	Codes from some car models after June 2000 can be read from Instrument Cluster too, but some Instrument Clusters are very hard to access and to read, or they must be scanned before getting access to the Cluster. Well, it will take too much time and sometimes it can be impossible i.e. Audi A4-2001+ (All remaining by OBD.)<br style="" />\r\n	In such cases we have a second possibility. We can read out the Login Code by OBD from Engine ECU. This Login Code in Engine ECU is the same as the Login Code in Instrument Cluster.<br style="" />\r\n	With this device you can read the security Login Code for VAG Cars starting at +/-June 2000 till 2004 with BOSCH ECU&#39;s EDC15/ME7.1/ME7.1.1/ME7.5. These ECU&#39;s are in the most engines of VAG Concern from +/-June 2000 till 2004.<br style="" />\r\n	Everything is based on K-Line Diagnostic VAG cars, so it doesn&#39;t work on Can Bus Diagnostic VAG, i.e. Golf-5, Touareg, etc.</font></p>\r\n', 1258291791, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 1, '1', 'no'),
(178, 35, '/uploads/images/Vag%20Diagnostic%20Kit/VAG%20K+CAN%20COMMANDER%20FULL%203.0.jpg', 'VAG K+CAN COMMANDER FULL 3.0', '<p>\r\n	<font style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial;">Diagnostic via CAN and Special functions via K-line. <br style="" />\r\n	Covers all electronic control units in vehicles (diagnostic addresses from 0x01 to 0x80). This can allow of user to investigate and diagnosis some new units untouchable for remaining diagnostic tools. Functions are under CAN-TP2.0. <br style="" />\r\n	Manual definition of running diagnostic session &iexcl;&iexcl;?&not;C not like remaining diagnostic tools always standard diagnostic session 0x89. Function is under CAN-TP2.0. <br style="" />\r\n	Broadcast diagnostic request &iexcl;&iexcl;?&not;C disable normal communication, clear DTCs, Logistic (transport) mode,.... Functions are under CAN-TP2.0. <br style="" />\r\n	Allows managing of brand new units (and immobilizer units) where is allowed programming of PIN, SKC, BGW, MAC. Functions are under CAN-TP2.0. <br style="" />\r\n	Most of popular diagnostic requests &iexcl;&iexcl;?&not;C identifications, coding, adaptations, DTCs and s.o. Functions are under CAN-TP2.0. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - odometer correction in instrument clusters and EDC15x. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - read Security Access Code/Login WFS. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - read/program immobilizer data. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - read/write EEPROM from instrument cluster/immobilizer. All supported clusters CAN/K. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - VAG MMI TV Activation. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - Read/Write EEPROM of Engine Control Units BOSCH VAG-EDC15x, VAG-ME7.1.1, VAG-Cartronic ME7.8,Porsche. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - Key learning buttons for easy usage (not needed security code). Can do component security authorization. <br style="" />\r\n	Special function - Key learning Porsche CAYENNE (not needed security code) K+CAN. <br